      "text": [
        "3967 - وَ قَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"اِشْتَرُوا وَ إِنْ كَانَ غَالِياً فَإِنَّ اَلرِّزْقَ يَنْزِلُ مَعَ اَلشِّرَاءِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3967 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Buy, even if it is expensive, for indeed sustenance descends with purchasing.\""
        ]
      }
    }
